Posts.Content: My current stats and confusing. 43 years old. PSA 3.9. Biopsy 3+3 G6 with 2 out of 12 cores positive. Less then 10% total volume. Endo Coil MRI didnt detect the cancer. I have NO INTEREST IN RP DaVinci and the SE. But Im confused how a biopsy says 1 thing and the MRI detects nothing? Pretty uncomfortable procedure to find nothing. Im at a Crossroads. Looking seriously at AS but surgeons recommends surgery. He states its very low risk but looking at my stats Im a Ideal AS player here I think. Why have that surgery at 43...
